<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l25">mıt <expan>Geılbr<ex>echt</ex></expan> von Püchıs vnd mıt <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den dıe <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dacht</expan> vnd ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l26">want geweſt ſınt . gütlıch berıcht ſein . vnd eẅch keins <expan>arge<ex>n</ex></expan> gewartt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l27">vnd mıt eẅch ʒu <expan>dıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> niht <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts vnd eẅch </ab>
